#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"success\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"success\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<video autoplay loop muted width=\"200\" height=\"200\" poster=\"https://tails.net/install/inc/success/start.png\">\n"
"  <source src=\"https://tails.net/install/inc/success/start.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n"
"</video>\n"
msgstr ""
"<video autoplay loop muted width=\"200\" height=\"200\" poster=\"https://tails.net/install/inc/success/start.png\">\n"
"  <source src=\"https://tails.net/install/inc/success/start.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n"
"</video>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"  <p class=\"big\">You made it!</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<div>\n"
"  <p class=\"big\">Sie haben es geschafft!</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  <p>You managed to start <span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">your new</span> Tails on your computer!</p>\n"
msgstr "  <p>Du hast es geschafft <span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">dein neues</span> Tails auf deinem Computer zu starten!</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  <p>Congratulations on staying safe :)</p>\n"
msgstr "  <p>Herzlichen Glückwunsch, dass Sie sicher geblieben sind :)</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  <p>To continue discovering Tails, read our [[documentation|doc]].</p>\n"
msgstr "  <p>Um Tails weiter zu entdecken, lesen Sie unsere [[Dokumentation|doc]].</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h1 id=\"wi-fi\" class=\"step\">Test your Wi-Fi</h1>\n"
msgstr "<h1 id=\"wi-fi\" class=\"step\">Ihr WLAN testen</h1>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Problems with Wi-Fi are unfortunately quite common in Tails and Linux in "
"general. To test if your Wi-Fi interface works in Tails:"
msgstr ""
"Probleme mit Wi-Fi sind in Tails und im Allgemeinen unter Linux leider recht "
"häufig. Um zu testen, ob Ihre Wi-Fi-Schnittstelle in Tails funktioniert:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Open the system menu in the top-right corner:"
msgstr "Klicken Sie auf das Systemmenü in der oberen rechten Ecke:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   [[!img doc/first_steps/desktop/system-with-wifi-only.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "   [[!img doc/first_steps/desktop/system-with-wifi-only.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Click [[!img lib/go-next.png link=\"no\" class=\"symbolic\" alt=\"\"]] on "
"the right of the **Wi-Fi** button."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   A list of available Wi-Fi networks appears below the **Wi-Fi** button.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"After establishing a connection to a local network, the *Tor Connection* "
"assistant appears to help you connect to the Tor network."
msgstr ""
"Nachdem eine Verbidung zu einem Lokalen Netzwerk hergestellt wurde, "
"erscheint der Assistent für die *Tor-Verbindung* um dir zu helfen, dich mit "
"dem Tor-Netzwerk zu verbinden."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   [[!img doc/anonymous_internet/tor/tor-connection.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "   [[!img doc/anonymous_internet/tor/tor-connection.png class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "   <div class=\"next\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"attack\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   <p>To learn more about the Tor network, go to [[Connecting to the Tor\n"
"   network|doc/anonymous_internet/tor]].</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   </div>\n"
msgstr "   </div>\n"

